Collection of useful scripts.


Installation/Uninstall
======================

make install
    - creates $HOME/bin, if necessary
    - copies all scripts to $HOME/bin

make link
    - creates $HOME/bin, if necessary
    - links all scripts from $HOME/bin to the project's files
    This is useful, if you are a developer of the scripts.

make uninstall
    - removes/deletes all scripts from $HOME/bin



Description
===========

makemp3.sh
     Encodes all wav-files in the current directory (and subfolders)
     to mp3-files and copies them to $HOME/MP3 directory.

snapback.sh <target-path>
     RSync- and hard-link-based backup script.



